<p><u>November</u></p>
<p>Peoples at last realize that it is not each other who are their enemys, But the ruthless forces of Imperialism and Capitalism, of Militarism of all sorts, Of Jingo Journalism that sows falshood, hatred and suspicion, Then this war will not have been fought in vain, Then Peace will not have been established in vain.</p>
<p>We hope that every one of you will go home carrying a message of good will, of conciliation, of enlightenment. Let all men in our new epoch go forth as missionaries<br/> of the new evangel, as interpreters between nation and nation.</p>
<p>The Valiant dead who once fought against each other, have long been sleeping as comrades side by side in the same earth. May the living who once fought against each other labour as comrades on this self same earth. This is</p>
